# Docker & Port 3000

- The Sentinel **web app runs via Docker** and is served on **port 3000**.
- When testing in the browser, building URLs, or referring to the running app, always use **http://localhost:3000**.
- Do **not** assume port 3001 or any other port unless the user explicitly specifies one.
